Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.67,0:00:05.29,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Raise your eyes you can see\Nshooting stars up in the night sky
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.35,0:00:13.25,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Raise your eyes you can see\Nshooting stars up in the night sky
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.59,0:00:33.31,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,One, two...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.31,0:00:36.29,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,The sound resonates\NInto my heart, so hard and deep
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.29,0:00:40.25,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,A field of stars spans endlessly\NAnd through it I carve a passageway
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.25,0:00:42.19,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,In step with time as generations change
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.19,0:00:44.22,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Close your eyes and listen closely
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.22,0:00:47.38,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Shooting stars stream on silently…\Nuntil the goodbye
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.29,0:00:50.29,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Keep the light inside of you,\Nnever give up don't ever lose
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.29,0:00:52.14,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Transcend time and you will prove,\Nthere is a special place for you
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.14,0:00:53.93,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,A blaze of glory is there,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.93,0:00:55.73,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,It's all a part of our estate;\Nlife is our story to create
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.75,0:01:01.64,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Raise your eyes you can see\Nshooting stars up in the night sky
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.64,0:01:05.56,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Wishes speak from ages old by voice of light\NThroughout the age, never fade away
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.56,0:01:09.29,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,A secret fire, a scream of light,\Nvoices calling through twilight
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.29,0:01:11.39,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Cast your thoughts to the wind,\Nhang your wishes on the moon
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.39,0:01:13.25,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Live your life with all your strength\Nfor dreams will reach you very soon
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.25,0:01:16.71,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Raise your eyes you can see\Nshooting stars up in the night sky
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.96,0:01:19.14,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Wishes speak from ages old\Nby voice of light
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.14,0:01:21.13,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Throughout the age,\Nnever fade away
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.29,0:01:24.68,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Someday your dream will find\Nits place somewhere
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.68,0:01:28.38,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Keep shining like a star
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.59,0:01:33.17,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Well, if you'll let me \Neat you, I'll tell you.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.38,0:01:42.56,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,The one who reigns!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.56,0:01:45.05,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Mask of flesh, all creation,\Nflap of wings...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.21,0:01:46.71,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,the one who carries\Nthe title of human!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.29,0:01:48.42,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,In the name of truth\Nand temperance,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.42,0:01:51.17,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,dig your claws into\Nthe wall of sinless dreams!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.92,0:01:53.26,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Destruction Spell 33...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.26,0:01:54.46,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Pale Fire Crash!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.71,0:02:01.57,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Good, at least this much of\Nmy powers are back... Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.59,0:02:07.55,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Ridiculous! It didn't even scratch him!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.09,0:02:13.63,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Hah! I know that trick!\NIt's a Soul Reaper spell, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.21,0:02:18.17,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,But yours is so weak.\NI felt nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.68,0:02:20.47,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Dammit!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.47,0:02:24.86,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,As I thought, my Kido hasn't recovered\Nenough to use a spell of that level.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.59,0:02:31.05,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,How many years has it been…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.29,0:02:33.71,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,since I last saw Karin cry…?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.13,0:02:39.30,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Until our mom died,\NKarin was a crybaby, just like Yuzu.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.29,0:02:44.55,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,After she died, Yuzu, who was\Nthe clever and responsible one,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.29,0:02:49.29,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,tried to fill in for our mom, and began\Nto take over the housekeeping.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.08,0:02:52.96,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Karin, who wasn't good\Nat much of anything,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.67,0:02:58.09,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,stopped crying altogether so\Nas not to worry the rest of us.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.29,0:03:01.29,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Even when she lost\Na fight with an upperclassman,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.55,0:03:04.29,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,or when she hit a ball through\Nthe window
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.29,0:03:05.59,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,of the principal's office and\Nwas reprimanded,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.00,0:03:09.71,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,or when she broke\Nher leg while hiking,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.63,0:03:12.55,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,she never cried once.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.59,0:03:18.55,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Karin…leave this to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.38,0:03:27.80,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Are you really a Soul Reaper?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.55,0:03:31.42,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Why don't you take off that human form?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.82,0:03:32.67,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?!!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.71,0:03:48.55,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Oh…did I…get him?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.30,0:03:52.13,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Huh…? He hit a Hollow…?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.29,0:03:55.08,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Can he see spirits…?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.50,0:03:59.25,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,No…maybe not…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.29,0:04:04.13,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,What's this…\Nhe just happened to hit me…?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.71,0:04:06.71,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I thought he could see me-
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.00,0:04:12.63,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,There… I got 'im…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.38,0:04:15.21,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I-Impossible…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.67,0:04:20.46,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,He shouldn't be seeing the Hollow,\Nmuch less hearing his voice…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.67,0:04:26.71,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,He's calmly facing down an enemy\Nhe cannot even sense…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.84,0:04:30.88,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Doesn't he have any fear…?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.63,0:04:35.34,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Damn…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.67,0:04:43.59,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Bet you can't touch me here!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.59,0:04:47.50,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,What are you going to do,\Nyou good-for-nothing Soul Reaper?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.59,0:04:51.50,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Don't just stand there!\NGet away! He's up in the air!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.46,0:04:55.37,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Transfer student… You can see ghosts?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.63,0:04:58.92,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Never mind about that!\NIn any case, at that distance…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.34,0:05:00.85,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,– Where is he?\N– What?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.67,0:05:04.13,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,He's flying isn't he?\NIn which direction?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.67,0:05:06.38,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,What good would knowing that do?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.59,0:05:09.55,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I'd do this…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.29,0:05:15.29,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Now, what shall I do…?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.55,0:05:19.92,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Shall I do a hit-and-run and\Nsnatch him like a falcon?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.71,0:05:27.34,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,What is this…?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.29,0:05:29.88,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Now…where is he…?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.42,0:05:32.92,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Right there!\NSwing down right there!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.75,0:05:45.13,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Now, give up.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.42,0:05:48.17,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Someone's on his way\Nto finish you off.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.09,0:05:54.21,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,What's so funny?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.21,0:05:59.10,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,No wonder you Soul Reapers,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.10,0:06:04.09,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,the whole bunch of you, are always…\Ngetting beaten by us!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.50,0:06:13.08,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like the shoe's\Non the other foot.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.59,0:06:17.72,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,You Soul Reapers take us too lightly.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.72,0:06:20.09,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,That's why you end up like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.21,0:06:28.71,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Now…who shall I start eating…?\NI think I'll save the guy for last.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.96,0:06:35.71,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,What…?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.09,0:06:38.67,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,T-This is crazy!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.67,0:06:42.59,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,You think you can solve all\Nyour problems with muscle?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.80,0:06:44.22,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,You muscle-headed idiot?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.38,0:06:49.71,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Ugh…This one's got such\Nsharp instincts…!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.59,0:06:53.56,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,This way, Chad! Kick the air above me!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.59,0:06:56.55,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Damn!!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.29,0:07:04.29,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,No! Not there! Up above!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.29,0:07:05.96,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,In the sky?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.21,0:07:07.29,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I have an idea!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.34,0:07:10.29,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Transfer student…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.63,0:07:15.29,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Will this really work?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.67,0:07:20.25,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. We'll utilize your strength\Nand my brains.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.38,0:07:22.42,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,What can I say…?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.80,0:07:24.59,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,This don't seem smart at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.05,0:07:26.72,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I don't have to take that from you!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.29,0:07:28.96,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go! In the direction of the tiger!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.84,0:07:30.80,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Which way is the tiger?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.42,0:07:32.71,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Humph! Left!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.05,0:07:33.99,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Left…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.99,0:07:35.29,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,You fool! That's too high!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.96,0:07:40.21,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, here we go.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.59,0:07:46.29,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,If I'm this far up in the air,\Nno electric pole will reach me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.29,0:07:47.09,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Fire!!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.29,0:07:52.48,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Give up!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.71,0:07:56.45,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,O-Okay…! I-I give up…!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.00,0:07:57.96,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Just kidding!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.00,0:08:10.92,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,W-What happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.29,0:08:15.38,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,S-Sorry about that.\NHe caught me by surprise.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.96,0:08:19.75,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Damn…! What in the world\Nare these… leeches?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.21,0:08:22.21,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Exactly!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.92,0:08:26.63,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,They won't come off easily…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.80,0:08:30.00,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Besides,\Nthey're my targets!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.92,0:08:36.96,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Transfer student…!?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.21,0:08:41.55,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,W-What happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.17,0:08:44.29,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Are you surprised?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.29,0:08:46.67,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Those leeches are small bombs.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.88,0:08:50.24,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,They respond to sounds from my tongue,\Nand explode!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.24,0:08:52.94,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Your guard was wide open.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.42,0:09:12.00,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,You wanna take me on, you lummox?\NBut you…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.06,0:09:13.75,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Oh!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.50,0:09:20.29,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I get it… He ran off a while ago to gain\Nsome time to bring this here…?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.96,0:09:24.92,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry, Mister…\NHe caught me…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.92,0:09:26.01,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Shibata…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.01,0:09:29.17,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like you understand now, big boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.21,0:09:34.29,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Now, it's time for us to play, Soul Reaper!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.80,0:09:40.06,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Now run! Let me enjoy hunting you down!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.13,0:09:46.42,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Don't move from here, Chad…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.13,0:09:51.29,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,If you take even a step,\Nhe plans to blow up that birdcage.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.09,0:09:55.09,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Transfer student, what about you?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.17,0:09:59.96,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,You needn't worry about me!\NI gave my word…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.29,0:10:02.29,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,not to foul up!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.30,0:10:04.29,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Your word?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.63,0:10:13.63,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,This is getting fun…!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.00,0:10:33.50,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,You're covered with them!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.38,0:10:49.34,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,How nice…to see you covered in blood.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.34,0:10:51.71,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,You're so pretty…!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.30,0:10:54.42,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I can hardly…wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.13,0:10:58.77,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, come on, come on, come on!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.29,0:11:01.29,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,How long do you intend\Nto keep running?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.50,0:11:04.31,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,You can turn around\Nand attack me, if you like!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.68,0:11:06.88,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Well?! Soul Reaper!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.13,0:11:14.95,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? What is it…?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.55,0:11:21.88,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Have you given up already?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.00,0:11:25.26,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,That's no fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.26,0:11:27.29,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, run, will you?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.88,0:11:29.34,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I haven't given up…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.17,0:11:33.05,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I have no need to run anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.29,0:11:34.38,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,What…?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.67,0:11:37.13,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,You said that I could\Nattack you, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.00,0:11:42.92,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,In that case,\NI will take you at your word.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.75,0:12:01.88,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,In that case,\NI will take you at your word.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.55,0:12:09.29,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Right…Ichigo…?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.71,0:12:12.59,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean,\N"Right, Ichigo"?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.13,0:12:16.01,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Didn't you promise to not worry me\Nby fouling up?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.29,0:12:20.80,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Fool! That's a line for someone who's\Neven a little bit worried, to say.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.96,0:12:23.96,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I guess you're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.46,0:12:26.80,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Damn you…!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.67,0:12:30.66,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,How long do you intend to\Nsit on my head!!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.17,0:12:33.84,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Ichigo Kurosaki, 15 years old!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.05,0:12:36.29,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Currently a surrogate Soul Reaper!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.29,0:12:40.18,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,If you want to chase someone,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.18,0:12:42.11,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,aren't you running after\Nthe wrong person?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.17,0:12:46.81,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Surrogate Soul Reaper…?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.71,0:12:50.24,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Damn!\NIf that's so…I should have…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.24,0:12:53.34,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,gone after you from the start!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.46,0:13:00.29,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Ichigo!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.05,0:13:08.43,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,You slowpoke!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.80,0:13:15.75,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,You look the tastiest…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.59,0:13:26.08,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I see. So you used those bombs\Nto pin Chad down
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.08,0:13:28.59,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,so you could enjoy attacking a girl?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.29,0:13:31.75,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,You're nothing but a stinking pig!!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.29,0:13:37.59,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,But now you're gonna be eaten\Nby that stinking pig.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.96,0:13:42.05,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I-Ichigo?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.96,0:13:44.29,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong, Ichigo?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.84,0:13:46.84,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Chad! Perfect timing.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.00,0:13:50.34,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Go and hide him and\Nthe parakeet somewhere safe.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.13,0:13:53.34,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Transfer student… What is this…?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.67,0:13:57.29,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry. He's now…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.58,0:13:59.30,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,in the middle of a battle!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.00,0:14:17.22,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Good move.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.22,0:14:20.97,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,But remember, the leeches,\Nthat flowed out of their bodies…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.97,0:14:23.80,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,are also bombs!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.80,0:14:41.46,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,There's something\NI want to ask you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.29,0:14:45.29,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Are you the one who\Nkilled the parents…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.29,0:14:47.42,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,of the kid inside the parakeet?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.05,0:14:52.88,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.27,0:14:55.42,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,He said it's all my fault.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.29,0:15:00.25,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Because of me, the man\Nand the girl got hurt.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.29,0:15:02.25,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Shibata…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.25,0:15:06.92,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,It's all because I wanted to bring\Nmy mom back to life.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.59,0:15:09.71,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.55,0:15:13.29,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I want my mom to come\Nback to life.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.17,0:15:14.76,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.76,0:15:15.38,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.38,0:15:17.64,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Did someone tell you…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.64,0:15:19.75,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,that he would bring\Nyour mother back to life?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.00,0:15:24.55,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Did someone tell you\Nthere was a way to do that?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.42,0:15:26.38,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.29,0:15:34.09,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I'm the one who killed\Nthat kid's mother – while I was still alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.63,0:15:39.31,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,At the time, I was a serial killer.\NIt was all over TV –
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.31,0:15:41.42,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I was famous.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.84,0:15:44.80,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,That kid's mother was my last victim.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.26,0:15:47.29,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,It was so much fun…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.29,0:15:49.59,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,She ran as hard as she could.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.00,0:15:55.23,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,She barely had any breath left,\Nbut she still tried to protect her kid.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.23,0:15:57.24,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,It was such a thrill.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.55,0:15:59.75,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,But that's where it went wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.21,0:16:02.85,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I chased her out onto her veranda…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.85,0:16:06.46,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,That kid!\NHe grabbed my shoe laces…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.63,0:16:12.29,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Who woulda thought I'd get killed\Nby a slip up like that…?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.80,0:16:18.21,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I decided to pay that kid back.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.55,0:16:23.29,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I put the soul of the boy, who survived,\Ninto the parakeet, and I told him this:
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.29,0:16:28.29,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Three months! If you can\Nrun around in that form for that long,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.29,0:16:32.30,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I would bring his mother back to life.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.30,0:16:33.64,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Bring her back to life…?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.64,0:16:39.42,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Fool! Of course, I couldn't do that –\Nbring a dead person back to life!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.29,0:16:42.14,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,But that kid believed me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.14,0:16:43.46,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,He ran as hard as he could.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.29,0:16:46.68,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,What's fun about this\Npenalty game is that
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.68,0:16:51.29,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I could kill off any and everyone\Nwho tried to protect the kid.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.55,0:16:55.68,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,And each time, the kid would whine\Nand beg to quit.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.68,0:16:58.29,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,He didn't like it, he said.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.60,0:17:00.74,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,That's when I used my clincher…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.74,0:17:04.57,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,"Your mother is waiting for\N you to save her!"
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.57,0:17:08.88,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Hearing that, he would\Nalways regain his will.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.13,0:17:12.34,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,He'd cry, "Mom…! Mom…!"
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.29,0:17:17.29,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,What are you sympathizing\Nwith him for?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.29,0:17:18.75,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,You dropped your guard!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.02,0:17:23.32,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,This is the end for you!!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.59,0:17:33.34,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,You can have this bomb back.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.34,0:17:38.09,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong?\NYou're going to set it off, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.96,0:17:41.13,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Come on and click your tongue!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.63,0:17:45.34,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Aren't you going to\Nclick your tongue?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.75,0:17:48.84,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,In that case…\NI'll take your tongue!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.88,0:17:53.38,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, my tongue!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.30,0:17:58.82,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Get lost…!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.88,0:18:19.63,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Wha..?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.17,0:18:21.92,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,It is Hell…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.35,0:18:26.32,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,The Zanpaku-to can only wash away\Nsins committed after death.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.29,0:18:31.29,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,For Hollows that committed major sins\Nbefore their death…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.29,0:18:33.30,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,the Gates of the Netherworld will open!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.38,0:19:14.34,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,So…he's gone to hell…?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.80,0:19:25.67,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Well…?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.59,0:19:27.80,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,It's unfortunate, but…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.17,0:19:31.67,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,his chain of fate has been severed;\Nthere's no sign of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.29,0:19:34.67,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,There's no way I can return him\Nto his body.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.17,0:19:36.00,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,No…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.71,0:19:38.46,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Shibata…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.00,0:19:44.29,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry!\NSoul Society isn't a scary place!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.50,0:19:50.13,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,You'll never get hungry,\Nand your body will feel light.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.29,0:19:53.09,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,You'll probably find it\Na better place than this!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.25,0:19:56.55,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Oh…? You can say that…\Nwhen you're just a hanger-on…?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.71,0:20:01.17,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,But, that might be true.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.92,0:20:04.85,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,At least, if you go over,\Nyou'll be able to see your mom.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.85,0:20:05.75,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Oh!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.38,0:20:08.97,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,You can't bring her\Nback to life,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.97,0:20:12.30,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,but now, you can go to her.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.29,0:20:15.25,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Ichigo…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.29,0:20:21.21,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Mister…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.13,0:20:23.55,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you for everything…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.67,0:20:30.50,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,You ran around with me in your arms,\Nso I didn't get hurt at all…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.29,0:20:33.24,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Yes… You're safe…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.84,0:20:40.55,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I'll be going, then.\NThank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.29,0:20:42.21,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Yuichi…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.50,0:20:47.67,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,When I die and pass over...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.09,0:20:51.42,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,would it be okay if I carried you\Nand ran around again?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.63,0:20:56.30,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.50,0:21:09.34,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Now, then…\NShall we get on with the Konso?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.50,0:21:29.67,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you…Ichigo…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.29,0:22:03.96,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Though the voyage must continue on
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.71,0:22:08.67,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,May seas always be calm
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.92,0:22:13.76,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,When the cycle of the moon\Nhas renewed may it shine
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.76,0:22:19.02,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,It's light to guide your boat
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.29,0:22:23.29,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I offer this voyage a prayer
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.63,0:22:28.30,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,With each new day that still awaits
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.59,0:22:32.67,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,On vividly shining seas
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.05,0:22:39.55,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,To the end of the journey
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.59,0:22:42.29,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Pardon me for the last time.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.71,0:22:45.17,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Kisuke Urahara,\Nowner of the Urahara Store.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.17,0:22:49.28,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to do my best to bring you\Nthe preview this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.28,0:22:51.39,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,The Urahara Store\Ngot its start when I…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.39,0:22:52.81,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,What are you talking about?!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.81,0:22:54.34,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I told you we don't have\Nmuch time, didn't I?!